====Usage notes====
* In Taiwan, both {{zh-l|*跡}} and {{zh-l|*蹟}} are standard forms. {{zh-l|*蹟}} is used in some compounds like {{zh-l|*奇蹟}} and {{zh-l|*事蹟}} (in which {{zh-l|*跡}} or {{zh-l|*迹}} are acceptable but could be seen as informal), while {{zh-l|*跡}} is used in others like {{zh-l|*痕跡}} and {{zh-l|*筆跡}} (in which {{zh-l|*跡}} should not be written as {{zh-l|*蹟}}).
* In Hong Kong, only {{zh-l|*跡}} is the standard form, while {{zh-l|*蹟}} and {{zh-l|*迹}} are acceptable variant forms.

